# security: linkpage core publishes ONLY index.html at root.
# Subdirs like vip-download/ and note-lp-*/ are managed manually
# (handled outside linkpage.py build/guard flow).
*
!index.html
!.gitignore
!vip-download/
!vip-download/**
!note-lp-sales/
!note-lp-sales/**
!note-lp-simple/
!note-lp-simple/**
!note-lp-edu/
!note-lp-edu/**
